{"id":608331,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Avakian","text":"George Mesrop Avakian (;; March 15, 1919 \u2013 November 22, 2017) was an American record producer, artist manager, writer, educator and executive. He was best known for his work from 1939 to the early-1960s at Decca Records, Columbia Records, Warner Bros. Records, and RCA Records. He was born in Armavir, Russia.\nAvakian worked with artists such as Louis Armstrong, Miles Davis, Duke Ellington, Benny Goodman, Dave Brubeck, Eddie Condon, Keith Jarrett, Erroll Garner, Buck Clayton, Sonny Rollins, Paul Desmond, Edith Piaf, Bob Newhart, Johnny Mathis, John Cage, Ravi Shankar, and many other notable jazz musicians and composers.\nAvakian died on November 22, 2017, aged 98, at his home in Manhattan, New York.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Decca_Records","surface_form":"Decca Records","offset":206},{"uri":"Columbia_Records","surface_form":"Columbia Records","offset":221},{"uri":"Warner_Bros._Records","surface_form":"Warner Bros. Records","offset":239},{"uri":"RCA_Records","surface_form":"RCA Records","offset":265},{"uri":"Armavir%2C_Russia","surface_form":"Armavir","offset":293},{"uri":"Russia","surface_form":"Russia","offset":302},{"uri":"Louis_Armstrong","surface_form":"Louis Armstrong","offset":346},{"uri":"Miles_Davis","surface_form":"Miles Davis","offset":363},{"uri":"Duke_Ellington","surface_form":"Duke Ellington","offset":376},{"uri":"Benny_Goodman","surface_form":"Benny Goodman","offset":392},{"uri":"Dave_Brubeck","surface_form":"Dave Brubeck","offset":407},{"uri":"Eddie_Condon","surface_form":"Eddie Condon","offset":421},{"uri":"Keith_Jarrett","surface_form":"Keith Jarrett","offset":435},{"uri":"Erroll_Garner","surface_form":"Erroll Garner","offset":450},{"uri":"Buck_Clayton","surface_form":"Buck Clayton","offset":465},{"uri":"Sonny_Rollins","surface_form":"Sonny Rollins","offset":479},{"uri":"Paul_Desmond","surface_form":"Paul Desmond","offset":494},{"uri":"Edith_Piaf","surface_form":"Edith Piaf","offset":508},{"uri":"Bob_Newhart","surface_form":"Bob Newhart","offset":520},{"uri":"Johnny_Mathis","surface_form":"Johnny Mathis","offset":533},{"uri":"John_Cage","surface_form":"John Cage","offset":548},{"uri":"Ravi_Shankar","surface_form":"Ravi Shankar","offset":559},{"uri":"Jazz","surface_form":"jazz","offset":596},{"uri":"Manhattan","surface_form":"Manhattan","offset":685},{"uri":"New_York","surface_form":"New York","offset":696}]}